            How to be a spy in the digital age
            The head of MI6 has just revealed a huge secret - his first ever missionBut more than 20 years on from that, the demands on agents have massively changed. It's no longer just a matter of trench coats, cocktails and false identities. So what does it take to be a spy in the digital age?Produced by Emily Wolstencroft.
                
